{magic_link}

accepted.body:
Hi {requester_name},

{receiver_name} accepted your meeting request at '{event_title}'.

When: {start_time} – {end_time}
Where: {location_name}{table_str}

Log in to chat or manage your schedule:
{magic_link}

declined.body:
Hi {requester_name},

{receiver_name} declined your meeting request at '{event_title}'.{reason_block}

You can log in to send a request to another attendee:
{magic_link}
